# MacOs alternative Latvian keyboard

Labots OS X "Latvian" klaviatūras izkārtojums, līdzīgs Windows "Latvian (QWERTY)" izkārtojumam. Veiktas sekojošās izmaiņas:
 - Novākts "dead key" no apostrofa
 - Shift+3 izvada "#" nevis "£"

Modified OS X "Latvian" keyboard layout that is very similar to the Windows "Latvian (QWERTY)" layout. The following changes have been made:
- No dead key on the apostrophe
- Shift+3 outputs "#" instead of "£"

## How to install

1. Clone this repo in some temporary directory
2. Open cloned directory in finder
3. Copy bundle to `/Library/Keyboard Layouts`
4. Restart your MAC and go "System settings" -> "Keyboard" -> "Input sources", hit `+` button, choose Latvian at left and alternative keyboard at right.
